Package: SSLAR
Title: SSLAR (Spatial Single-cell Labeling and Annotation using Reference)
Version: 0.9
Authors@R: 
    person("Feixiang", "Wang", , "wfxcode@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre","com"))
Description: The SSLAR performs spatial single-cell labeling and annotation using a reference dataset. It integrates single-cell RNA sequencing (scRNA-seq) data with spatial transcriptomics (ST) data to infer cell type proportions in each spatial location (spot).
